<div id="pf65" class="pf wa hb" data-page-no="65"><div class="pc pc65 wa hb"><div class="t m7e2 xc h16 ybf9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 13 September 21-27 </div><div class="t m88b x3 h3f y441 ff1 fs21 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m88c x4 h40 y441 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">171</div><div class="t m88d x95 h40 y441 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m253 x41 h40 y441 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">n2 </div><div class="t m13f x5e h3b y493 ff2 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">51.aff2Erfing5 </div><div class="t m88e x47 h40 y509 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.112m.115 </div><div class="t m7b7 xee h16 y50b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Consider him who endured from </div><div class="t m3ce xee h16 y446 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">iners such hostility against himself, </div><div class="t m83c x0 h16 y51d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that you may not grow weary or </div><div class="t m171 xee h16 y448 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">int-hearted. In your struggle against </div><div class="t m88f xee h13 y9e ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">i </div><div class="t mfa x4b h16 y2d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you have not yet resisted to the </div><div class="t m890 xee h16 y50d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)int of shedding your blood&quot; (Heb. </div><div class="t m3cb x51 h16 y50e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">:3, 4, RSV). </div><div class="t m4b3 x51 h16 ybfa ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In a very real sense, Job was a type of </div><div class="t m21a x51 h16 y44d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e suffering Saviour, and his </div><div class="t m891 x51 h16 y985 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perience was an example of the </div><div class="t md8 xee h16 y44f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">introversy between Christ and </div><div class="t m722 x51 h16 ya6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tan. </div><div class="t m892 x51 h16 y50f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Very early in the history of the </div><div class="t m832 xee h16 y525 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Drld is given the life record of one </div><div class="t m602 x51 h16 y510 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)b] over whom this controversy of </div><div class="t m509 x51 h16 y453 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tan&apos;s was </div><div class="t m69 x54 h16 y453 ffa fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">waged.&quot;—Education, </div><div class="t m5f9 xc1 h16 y453 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t m1f7 x51 h16 y511 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m158 x51 h16 y512 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is altogether appropriate, at the </div><div class="t m5b1 x51 h16 y39 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3se of this series of lessons, to take a </div><div class="t m6fd x51 h16 y513 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ok at the great Sufferer of whom Job </div><div class="t m893 x51 h16 y514 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is a type. </div><div class="t m50c x51 h16 y9d6 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Christ&apos;s situation and Job&apos;s are </div><div class="t m162 x51 h16 y515 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">uch alike. Job on his ash heap, Christ </div><div class="t m500 x4b h16 y458 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His cross. Job bears the pain and </div><div class="t m757 x51 h16 y686 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e public reproach of black leprosy, </div><div class="t m193 x51 h16 y516 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Irist of crucifixion. Each is </div><div class="t m8d x52 h16 y517 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rrounded by a jeering, irresponsible </div><div class="t m894 x51 h16 yb8 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bble. . . . </div><div class="t m704 x51 h16 y52f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Christ suffers the same unjust </div><div class="t m895 x51 h16 y530 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sapproval of the mob, &apos;His </div><div class="t m813 x52 h16 ybfb ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pearance was . . . marred.&apos; Isaiah </div><div class="t m440 x52 h16 y518 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">:14. So each man, Job and the </div><div class="t m5b2 x51 h16 y9da ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">aster, is accused of evil on the basis </div><div class="t m1b6 x51 h16 yace ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at his physical condition testifies to </div><div class="t m5f6 x51 h16 y533 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">raven&apos;s condemnation. . . . - </div><div class="t m376 x51 h16 yc0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Like the mob which followed </div><div class="t m694 x51 h16 y535 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Irist to His trial and to His </div><div class="t m10e x51 h16 y536 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ucifixion, the people about Job exult </div><div class="t m896 x0 h16 yc9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the opportunity to mistreat a </div><div class="t m745 x52 h16 y538 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perior. . . . </div><div class="t m897 x37 h16 yacf ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. . When Job intervenes for his </div><div class="t m593 x51 h16 y329 ffa fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ree </div><div class="t m853 x32 h16 y329 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">friends, who have augmented </div><div class="t m2e2 x21 h16 y53b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sorrow as we sinners grieve our </div><div class="t m402 x52 h16 y9dc ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ediator, his action becomes a high </div><div class="t m4f5 x52 h16 yd0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Duntain of evidence that he is a type  </div><div class="t m538 xaa h16 y498 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ.... Job is </div><div class="t m898 xcc h14 y498 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a </div><div class="t m13b xa7 h16 y498 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mediator; Christ </div><div class="t m899 xaa h16 yb32 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is </div><div class="t m83 x90 h16 yb32 ffa fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the </div><div class="t m375 x2c h16 y2b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mediator. </div><div class="t m82 x90 h16 ybfc ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Job&apos;s willingness to pray for his </div><div class="t m16a xaa h16 yb02 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">opponents climaxes his </div><div class="t m210 xaa h16 yb17 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">demonstration of loyalty to God. The </div><div class="t m7c8 xaa h16 yb18 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accusations of these men have been </div><div class="t m239 xaa h16 y44a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salt in his wounds. At the close of the </div><div class="t m891 xaa h16 y44b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ordeal his prayer in their behalf </div><div class="t m154 xaa h16 y44c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foreshadows the Saviour&apos;s prayer from </div><div class="t m3b4 xaa h16 yb34 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the cross, &apos;Father, forgive them; for </div><div class="t m4e1 xaa h16 y44e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they know not what they do.&apos; Luke </div><div class="t m3dd xaa h16 ybfd ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">23:34. Thus Job prays for his </div><div class="t m122 xaa h16 y450 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecutors .&quot;—Pau IT. Gibbs, </div><div class="t m3d0 xdc h16 y450 ffa fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job </div><div class="t m89a xb4 h14 y450 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t mdb xaa h16 y30c ffa fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the </div><div class="t m698 xd2 h14 y75f ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mysteries of Wisdom, </div><div class="t m16b x19 h16 y30c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 138-140. </div><div class="t m89b x93 h16 y451 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our lesson this week we look at </div><div class="t m785 xaa h16 yb54 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus to see the suffering He passed </div><div class="t m89c xaa h16 ybfe ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through while achieving our salvation. </div><div class="t m15e xaa h16 yb1c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He left heaven and came down to this </div><div class="t m22f xaa h16 yb55 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">earth to become a man and to live as a </div><div class="t m3eb xaa h16 yb1e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man. </div><div class="t m22d x90 h16 y454 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He came to His own creation, to His </div><div class="t m89d xaa h16 y455 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">own chosen people; yet He was </div><div class="t m348 xaa h16 y456 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rejected and despised. And in </div><div class="t m89e xaa h16 y457 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gethsemane He suffered the </div><div class="t m2d0 xaa h16 y77 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">separation from His Father. </div><div class="t m2bd x93 h16 y459 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the cross we have the supreme </div><div class="t mf xaa h16 y45a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">example of sacrifice. When we </div><div class="t m41b xaa h16 y45b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognize that Jesus did all this so that </div><div class="t m5e2 xaa h16 y45c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you and I can be saved, our hearts melt </div><div class="t m188 xaa h16 y52f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in love. The suffering that Jesus </div><div class="t mca xaa h16 y45e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">endured for us is called to mind by the </div><div class="t m196 xaa h16 y988 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feet-washing service and the bread </div><div class="t m6d xb h16 y518 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and wine of the Lord&apos;s Supper. </div><div class="t m29b xaa h16 y519 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 xaa h16 y462 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t md9 x56 h16 y533 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Became Man </div><div class="t m862 x56 h16 yc0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gal. 4:4, 5) </div><div class="t m65 xaa h16 y535 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t me x56 h16 y535 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Lived As Man </div><div class="t m89f x56 h16 y536 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Heb. 2:16, 17) </div><div class="t m67 xaa h16 y537 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m325 x56 h16 yc9 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Suffered and </div><div class="t m8a0 x56 h16 y538 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Died As Man </div><div class="t m183 x56 h16 y539 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 1:11) </div><div class="t m69 xb h16 y53a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m8a1 x56 h16 y53a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of Humiliation </div><div class="t m8c x56 h16 y53b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 13:12) </div><div class="t m6b xb h16 y46a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m1f7 x56 h16 y53c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of a Body </div><div class="t m4ee x56 h16 yd0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 22:19) </div><div class="t m6d xb h16 y46b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2e7 x56 h16 y53d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of Blood </div><div class="t m4ee x56 h16 yad0 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 22:20) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
